reviewText: My pittie looks so handsome in his collar.  Only 4 stars, as it seems to get loose on him, not sure if the material stretches after a while, but he got lots of compliments in his group obedience class, as he did have the best looking collar!
This video is really well made. For every acupuncturist and/or veterinarian, a great tool to teach clients where to give pressure massage for healing.
